{"tid":1023984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暖心3少年告白全校女生！情人節湊零用錢買300朵康乃馨，女老師也都有","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T08:48:33.000Z","uid":212399,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3c1a06e4764929340511fa951db8e0d9d69602","tid":1023984,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/3899538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2F3899538.jpg&h=aa2604b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n情人節剛過，各位是否也都有收到美麗的花呢？<br />\n美國肯薩斯州一間名為「Summit Trail Middle School」的學校，情人節當天，有三個少年自掏腰包一起買了300餘朵康乃馨，他們把花放在桶子裡，站在校園中庭，打算一朵接一朵地送給全校所有的女性，不論是女學生或是女教師，人人都能拿到一朵康乃馨。<br />\n三位男孩名為Tristan Valentine、Kyan Rice、Lincoln Holmes，他們這項計畫並沒有事先讓同學老師知道，也瞞著爸爸媽媽，他們存了好一陣子的零用錢，才湊齊買花的錢。<br />\n把花一一交到學校女性的手中，Tristan Valentine、Kyan Rice、Lincoln Holmes感到很開心，他們說，「希望每一位女性都能在情人節當天感到自己是重要的、特別的。」<br />\n校方事後也大大地表揚三位少年，認為他們的行為很成熟、很懂得尊重女性。<br />\n寫到此，各位怎麼看呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/3899540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2F3899540.jpg&h=1da272c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/3899539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2F3899539.jpg&h=668c042a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F41739&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=b5e7c9da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41739</a>"},{"pid":"3f2aaae2f26726caf00f0d26e02405abebaeebef","tid":1023984,"uid":54622,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"搞灣晒個party <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs